00063 /*
00064  * INT_ARRAY symbol table structures and prototypes
00065  */
00066 typedef struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol
00067 {
00068   int *int_array;               /* int array values of symbol */
00069   int array_length;             /* Length of int_array */
00070   unsigned int hash_val;        /* Hashed value of int_array */
00071   void *data;                   /* Data struct pointed to */
00072   struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol_Table *table; /* For deletion of symbol */
00073   struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol *next_hash;   /* For table's hash table */
00074   struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol *prev_hash;
00075   struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol *next_symbol; /* For table's contents list */
00076   struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol *prev_symbol;
00077 
00078 }
00079 INT_ARRAY_Symbol;
00080 
00081 typedef struct INT_ARRAY_Symbol_Table
00082 {
00083   char *name;                   /* For error messages */
00084   INT_ARRAY_Symbol **hash;      /* Array of size hash_size */
00085   int hash_size;                /* Must be power of 2 */
00086   int hash_mask;                /* AND mask, (hash_size - 1) */
00087   int resize_size;              /* When reached, resize hash table */
00088   INT_ARRAY_Symbol *head_symbol;        /* Contents list */
00089   INT_ARRAY_Symbol *tail_symbol;
00090   int symbol_count;
00091 }
00092 INT_ARRAY_Symbol_Table;
